text: Hey Josh. I hope you're doing well and that your family's safe in the current situation.

Access VFX released a podcast regarding jobhunting and the ongoing situation with CoViD-19. There's a lot of turmoil at the moment, but it might be interesting to hear how to deal with some of this regarding the industry: <https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8dI3ZkDm2sY>
